Fix for http://bugs.adobe.com/jira/browse/SDK-29426. The width/height in the default state wasn't saved when switching back and forth from another state with percent width/height. The fix is to associate percentWidth/Height with explicitWidth/Height when saving old values. We were only associating explicitWidth/Height with percentWidth/Height and not vice versa.
